GUI to automate image classification using CNN and Computer
Vision
How this GUI works?
 Execute the python code which uses tkinter in Jupyter notebook. New GUI window appears
after calling the mainloop.
 Import the data by clicking on ‘Import Data’ button. This helps you to browse through the
system and select the data file.
 Select the image to be classified.
 Predict the image category by clicking on ‘Predict’ button using the model saved.
Window 1: GUI window generated using tkinter after calling the mainloop.
Window 2: Selecting the image to be used for the project.
Window 3: Predict the category of the image.
Window 4: Image categorised correctly.
